{
  "texts": [
    "Every spoken language has its own sign language.",
    "While creating a dataset in Turkish sign language, which has a unique grammar and hand sign, we aimed to create a unique dataset under the provision of an expert.",
    "All images are taken from 6 different volunteers with the CANON 700d camera capable of taking 18 megapixel images.",
    "Each image in the dataset is used with its original dimensions of 5184 9 3456.",
    "Figure 7 shows RGB images of all digit movements in Turkish sign language, which is part of the dataset.In order to make the experimental dataset more diverse, the hand position and angle are constantly changed and 25 different images are taken from each volunteer for each number, and a Turkish sign language dataset is created."
  ]
}